      "content": "but what if they don't come back? what if this is just it? i'm just existing, not living. it feels like i'm just a ghost haunting a life that doesn't belong to me anymore. sometimes i think the only way to actually stop feeling this weight is to just... stop. to not have to fight the silence anymore. it seems like the only logical way to find peace.",
